== Care ==

Goats require very good fencing.  A fence that will hold a horse will not work for a goat.

== Uses ==

Goats eat many kinds of food, turning [[waste]] into milk, [[meat]] and [[fertilizer]] ([[manure]]).

Goat milk has a distinctive, gamey flavor. It is believed by some to offer health benefits.

Curried goat is a very popular dish in many parts of the world, including Jamaica, Indonesia, Malaysia and India.

